{
  "video_id": "U51MSK6nSQE",
  "title": "The case for a decentralized internet | Tamas Kocsis",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13200.0,
      "end_time": 14440.0,
      "text": "Three years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14480.0,
      "end_time": 17496.0,
      "text": "I started building a decentralized web"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17520.0,
      "end_time": 20800.0,
      "text": "because I was worried about the future of our internet."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21680.0,
      "end_time": 24296.0,
      "text": "The current internet we are using is about gatekeepers."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24320.0,
      "end_time": 26696.0,
      "text": "If you want to reach something on the web,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26720.0,
      "end_time": 29960.0,
      "text": "then you need to go through multiple middlemen."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29120.0,
      "end_time": 31576.0,
      "text": "First, a domain name server,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31600.0,
      "end_time": 34136.0,
      "text": "then a server hosting company,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34160.0,
      "end_time": 37895.0,
      "text": "which usually points you to a third party,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37920.0,
      "end_time": 39880.0,
      "text": "to a web hosting service."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 41800.0,
      "end_time": 44600.0,
      "text": "And this happens every time you want to reach a website on the web."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 45440.0,
      "end_time": 49896.0,
      "text": "But these gatekeepers are vulnerable to internet attacks"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 49920.0,
      "end_time": 53720.0,
      "text": "and also makes the censorship and the surveillance easier."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 55400.0,
      "end_time": 56760.0,
      "text": "And the situation is getting worse."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 57840.0,
      "end_time": 59536.0,
      "text": "Everything is moving to the cloud,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 59560.0,
      "end_time": 62640.0,
      "text": "where the data is hosted by giant corporations."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 63400.0,
      "end_time": 67679.0,
      "text": "This move creates much, much more powerful middlemen."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 68560.0,
      "end_time": 70856.0,
      "text": "Now, move to the cloud makes sense"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 70880.0,
      "end_time": 72936.0,
      "text": "because this way it&#39;s easier and cheaper"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 72960.0,
      "end_time": 75950.0,
      "text": "for the developers and the service operators."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 75120.0,
      "end_time": 79320.0,
      "text": "They don&#39;t have to worry about maintaining the physical servers."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 80720.0,
      "end_time": 85936.0,
      "text": "I can&#39;t blame them, but I found this trend to be very dangerous,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 85960.0,
      "end_time": 88216.0,
      "text": "because this way, these giant corporations"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 88240.0,
      "end_time": 92800.0,
      "text": "have unlimited control over the hosting services."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 92920.0,
      "end_time": 95920.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s very easy to abuse this power."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 97440.0,
      "end_time": 101216.0,
      "text": "For example, last year, a CEO of a company"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 101240.0,
      "end_time": 105856.0,
      "text": "that acts as a gatekeeper for nine million websites"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 105880.0,
      "end_time": 107976.0,
      "text": "decided, after some public pressure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 108000.0,
      "end_time": 110416.0,
      "text": "that one of the sites it manages,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 110440.0,
      "end_time": 113390.0,
      "text": "a far right page, should be blocked."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 114520.0,
      "end_time": 117399.0,
      "text": "He then sent an internal email to his coworkers."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 119000.0,
      "end_time": 121200.0,
      "text": "\"This was an arbitrary decision."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 122640.0,
      "end_time": 125176.0,
      "text": "I woke up this morning in a bad mood"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 125200.0,
      "end_time": 127840.0,
      "text": "and decided to kick them off the Internet.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 129960.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131856.0,
      "text": "Even he admits,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 131880.0,
      "end_time": 133920.0,
      "text": "\"No one should have this power.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 135720.0,
      "end_time": 138616.0,
      "text": "As a response, one of the employees asked him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 138640.0,
      "end_time": 141279.0,
      "text": "\"Is this the day the Internet dies?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 143800.0,
      "end_time": 146216.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t think we are actually killing the internet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 146240.0,
      "end_time": 148176.0,
      "text": "but I do think that we are in the middle"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 148200.0,
      "end_time": 150976.0,
      "text": "of a kind of irresponsible centralization process"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 151000.0,
      "end_time": 153640.0,
      "text": "that makes our internet more fragile."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 155120.0,
      "end_time": 158456.0,
      "text": "The decentralized, people-to-people web"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 158480.0,
      "end_time": 161536.0,
      "text": "solves this problem by removing the central points,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 161560.0,
      "end_time": 163160.0,
      "text": "the web-hosting services."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 163880.0,
      "end_time": 166136.0,
      "text": "It empowers the users"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 166160.0,
      "end_time": 169680.0,
      "text": "to have host sites they want to preserve."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 171800.0,
      "end_time": 176280.0,
      "text": "On this network, the sites get downloaded directly from other visitors."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 177120.0,
      "end_time": 179456.0,
      "text": "This means, if you have a site with 100 visitors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 179480.0,
      "end_time": 182679.0,
      "text": "then it&#39;s hosted [by] 100 computers around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 184400.0,
      "end_time": 189400.0,
      "text": "Basically, this is a people-powered version of the internet."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 190720.0,
      "end_time": 194736.0,
      "text": "The security of the network is provided by public-key cryptography."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 194760.0,
      "end_time": 198256.0,
      "text": "This makes sure that no one can modify the sites"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 198280.0,
      "end_time": 199960.0,
      "text": "but only the real owner."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 201360.0,
      "end_time": 205816.0,
      "text": "Think of it like instead of getting electricity from big power plants,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 205840.0,
      "end_time": 207896.0,
      "text": "you put solar panels on top of your house,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 207920.0,
      "end_time": 210815.0,
      "text": "and if your neighbor down the street needs some extra energy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 210840.0,
      "end_time": 213520.0,
      "text": "then they can just download some from your house."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 216760.0,
      "end_time": 219576.0,
      "text": "So by using the decentralized web,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 219600.0,
      "end_time": 223920.0,
      "text": "we can help to keep content accessible for other visitors."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 224800.0,
      "end_time": 227496.0,
      "text": "And by that, it means"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 227520.0,
      "end_time": 231176.0,
      "text": "that we can also fight against things"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 231200.0,
      "end_time": 232839.0,
      "text": "that we feel are unjust,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 234000.0,
      "end_time": 235200.0,
      "text": "like censorship."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 236480.0,
      "end_time": 239399.0,
      "text": "In China, the internet is tightly controlled."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 240600.0,
      "end_time": 244456.0,
      "text": "They can&#39;t criticize the government,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 244480.0,
      "end_time": 246495.0,
      "text": "organize a protest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 246520.0,
      "end_time": 249256.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s also forbidden to post"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 249280.0,
      "end_time": 253840.0,
      "text": "a kind of emoticon to remember the victims of the Tiananmen Square Massacre."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 255400.0,
      "end_time": 258101.0,
      "text": "With the decentralized web, it&#39;s not the government that decides"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 258125.0,
      "end_time": 260120.0,
      "text": "what gets seen and what doesn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 261790.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263960.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 263120.0,
      "end_time": 265280.0,
      "text": "which makes the web more democratic."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 266600.0,
      "end_time": 269160.0,
      "text": "But at the same time, it&#39;s hard to use this network"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 269400.0,
      "end_time": 271815.0,
      "text": "to do something that is clearly illegal"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 271839.0,
      "end_time": 273216.0,
      "text": "everywhere in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 273240.0,
      "end_time": 276776.0,
      "text": "as the users probably don&#39;t want to endanger themselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 276800.0,
      "end_time": 279280.0,
      "text": "hosting these kinds of problematic content."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 281720.0,
      "end_time": 284656.0,
      "text": "Another increasing threat"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 284680.0,
      "end_time": 286440.0,
      "text": "to internet freedom"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 287400.0,
      "end_time": 288840.0,
      "text": "is overregulation."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 291160.0,
      "end_time": 293256.0,
      "text": "I have the impression"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 293280.0,
      "end_time": 294976.0,
      "text": "that our delegates"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 295000.0,
      "end_time": 297856.0,
      "text": "who vote on the internet regulation laws"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 297880.0,
      "end_time": 301800.0,
      "text": "are not fully aware of their decisions."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 301760.0,
      "end_time": 305416.0,
      "text": "For example, the European Parliament has a new law on the table,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 305440.0,
      "end_time": 307416.0,
      "text": "a new copyright protection law,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 307440.0,
      "end_time": 310800.0,
      "text": "that has a part called Article 13."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 311680.0,
      "end_time": 316160.0,
      "text": "If it passes, it would require every big website"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 316400.0,
      "end_time": 318296.0,
      "text": "to implement a filter"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 318320.0,
      "end_time": 321616.0,
      "text": "that automatically blocks content"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 321640.0,
      "end_time": 324560.0,
      "text": "based on rules controlled by big corporations."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 325800.0,
      "end_time": 328456.0,
      "text": "The original idea is to protect copyrighted materials,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 328480.0,
      "end_time": 331976.0,
      "text": "but it would endanger many other things we do on the internet:"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 332000.0,
      "end_time": 335520.0,
      "text": "blogging, criticizing, discussing, linking and sharing."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 336760.0,
      "end_time": 340575.0,
      "text": "Google and YouTube already have similar systems"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 340600.0,
      "end_time": 345880.0,
      "text": "and they are receiving 100,000 takedown requests every hour."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 347440.0,
      "end_time": 350656.0,
      "text": "Of course, they can&#39;t process this amount of data by hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 350680.0,
      "end_time": 352336.0,
      "text": "so they are using machine learning"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 352360.0,
      "end_time": 354920.0,
      "text": "to decide if it&#39;s really a copyright violation or not."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 356600.0,
      "end_time": 360400.0,
      "text": "But these filters do make mistakes."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 361000.0,
      "end_time": 366816.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re removing everything from documentation of human rights abuses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 366840.0,
      "end_time": 369736.0,
      "text": "lectures about copyrights"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 369760.0,
      "end_time": 371976.0,
      "text": "and search results"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 372000.0,
      "end_time": 377400.0,
      "text": "that point to criticism of this new Article 13."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 378840.0,
      "end_time": 381599.0,
      "text": "Beside of that, they are also removing many other things."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 384480.0,
      "end_time": 390776.0,
      "text": "And sometimes, these filters aren&#39;t just removing the specific content,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 390800.0,
      "end_time": 395576.0,
      "text": "but it could also lead to loss of your linked accounts:"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 395600.0,
      "end_time": 399776.0,
      "text": "your email address, your documents, your photos,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 399800.0,
      "end_time": 401976.0,
      "text": "or your unfinished book,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 402000.0,
      "end_time": 404720.0,
      "text": "which happened with the writer Dennis Cooper."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 405920.0,
      "end_time": 410416.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not hard to see how a system like this could be abused"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 410440.0,
      "end_time": 413640.0,
      "text": "by politicians and corporate competitors."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 415760.0,
      "end_time": 422560.0,
      "text": "This Article 13, the extension of these automated filters to the whole internet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 422800.0,
      "end_time": 424216.0,
      "text": "got strong opposition"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 424240.0,
      "end_time": 429616.0,
      "text": "from Wikipedia, Github, Mozilla, and many others,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 429640.0,
      "end_time": 435176.0,
      "text": "including the original founders of the internet and the World Wide Web,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 435200.0,
      "end_time": 437800.0,
      "text": "Vint Cerf and Tim Berners-Lee."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 438120.0,
      "end_time": 441160.0,
      "text": "But despite this strong opposition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 441400.0,
      "end_time": 443416.0,
      "text": "on the last European Parliament vote,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 443440.0,
      "end_time": 447320.0,
      "text": "two thirds of the representatives supported this law."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 449800.0,
      "end_time": 451800.0,
      "text": "The final vote will be early 2019."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 452920.0,
      "end_time": 454896.0,
      "text": "The result is important,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 454920.0,
      "end_time": 457616.0,
      "text": "but whatever happens,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 457640.0,
      "end_time": 462936.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m pretty sure it will be followed by many other similar proposals"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 462960.0,
      "end_time": 464159.0,
      "text": "around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 465280.0,
      "end_time": 468455.0,
      "text": "These kinds of regulations would be very hard to enforce"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 468480.0,
      "end_time": 469936.0,
      "text": "through a decentralized web,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 469960.0,
      "end_time": 472239.0,
      "text": "as there is no hosting companies."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 473280.0,
      "end_time": 476280.0,
      "text": "The websites are served by the visitors themselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 478240.0,
      "end_time": 481920.0,
      "text": "I started to build this network three years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 483120.0,
      "end_time": 487376.0,
      "text": "Since then, I&#39;ve spent thousands, tens of thousands of hours"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 487400.0,
      "end_time": 488599.0,
      "text": "on the development."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 489800.0,
      "end_time": 491376.0,
      "text": "Why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 491400.0,
      "end_time": 495176.0,
      "text": "Why would anyone spend thousands of hours on something anyone can freely copy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 495200.0,
      "end_time": 497400.0,
      "text": "rename, or even sell?"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 499600.0,
      "end_time": 501336.0,
      "text": "Well, in my case,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 501360.0,
      "end_time": 503800.0,
      "text": "one of the reasons was to do something meaningful."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 504720.0,
      "end_time": 507256.0,
      "text": "During my daily regular job as a web developer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 507280.0,
      "end_time": 510496.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t have the feeling that I&#39;m working on something"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 510520.0,
      "end_time": 513159.0,
      "text": "that had a chance to be a bigger than me."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 515000.0,
      "end_time": 518816.0,
      "text": "Simply, I just wanted to make my short presence in this world"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 518840.00000000006,
      "end_time": 520400.00000000006,
      "text": "to be meaningful."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 523000.0,
      "end_time": 528800.0,
      "text": "Last year, the Great Firewall of China started blocking this network I created."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 529400.0,
      "end_time": 532655.0,
      "text": "This move officially made me the enemy"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 532679.0,
      "end_time": 536120.0,
      "text": "of the government-supported internet censorship."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 537680.0,
      "end_time": 540695.0,
      "text": "Since then, it&#39;s been really a game of cat and mouse."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 540720.0,
      "end_time": 543456.0,
      "text": "They make new rules in the firewall"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 543480.0,
      "end_time": 546496.0,
      "text": "and I try to react to it as fast as I can"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 546520.0,
      "end_time": 550616.0,
      "text": "so the users can keep hosting content and create websites"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 550640.0,
      "end_time": 556000.0,
      "text": "that otherwise would be censored by the centralized Chinese internet."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 557680.0,
      "end_time": 561760.0,
      "text": "My other motivation to create this network was worry."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 563800.0,
      "end_time": 568296.0,
      "text": "I fear that the future of our internet is out of our control."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 568320.0,
      "end_time": 571736.0,
      "text": "The increasing centralization and the proposed laws"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 571760.0,
      "end_time": 574295.0,
      "text": "are threatening our freedom of speech"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 574320.0,
      "end_time": 576560.0,
      "text": "and, by that, our democracy."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 577440.0,
      "end_time": 580776.0,
      "text": "So for me, building a decentralized web"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 580800.0,
      "end_time": 584160.0,
      "text": "means creating a safe harbor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 584400.0,
      "end_time": 590856.0,
      "text": "a space where the rules are not written by big corporations and political parties,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 590880.0,
      "end_time": 592640.0,
      "text": "but by the people."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 593840.0,
      "end_time": 595560.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 595800.0,
      "end_time": 599480.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}